      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 19,
      "message": "Well, this approach - it does not allow setting different repository for a specific image.\nI think that the better solution is to make it in values.yaml, like this:\n  sparkyBeImage: \"{{ .Values.repository.onap }}/openecomp/sparky-be\"\nAnd then in the deployment manifest:\n        image: \"{{tpl $.Values.image.sparky .}}\"\nIt, however, requires at helm 2.5 and up. But it will allow to specify different repository for e.g. sparkyBeImage.",
